          <versionCode>00</versionCode>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Benefit Adjustment of Social Security Income Compensation Act or the BASIC Act</strong></p> <p>This bill requires the Social Security Administration (SSA) to continue monthly insurance benefit payments to a beneficiary, on a prorated basis,&nbsp;through the month of the beneficiary's death. The bill also revises the SSA's methodology for calculating certain lump-sum payments to survivors.<br /></p>]]></text>
